<list>
<li>Fixed bug causing a directory to be created when creating a named directory through the writable menu field on RISC&nbsp;OS&nbsp;3.
</list>


<subhead title="1.10 (6 December 2002)">

Public Beta release.

<list>
<li>Module converted to new format and checked for 32-bit compatibility.
</list>


<subhead title="1.11 (2 February 2014)">

<list>
<li>Converted source to ObjAsm format and checked for ARMv7 compatibility.
</list>

